>>>>[BACKGROUND MUSIC] And
I think many people today

00:00:14.890 --> 00:00:16.490 align:middle line:84%
don't know what to
believe anymore.

00:00:16.490 --> 00:00:18.114 align:middle line:84%
>>People are basically
going to keep on

00:00:18.114 --> 00:00:21.060 align:middle line:84%
to help uncover what
really happened.

00:00:21.060 --> 00:00:23.320 align:middle line:84%
>>I felt like something
was watching me.

00:00:23.320 --> 00:00:25.040 align:middle line:84%
>>We weren't given
